OL,3,CGuernsey's electricity bills set to
OL,4,Crise by 10% this summer
OL,6,FPresident of the STSB, Deputy Peter
OL,7,FRoffey, said the rise follows years of
OL,8,Funderfunding: "We have fortunately
OL,9,Favoided the crippling increases in
OL,10,Fenergy bills that have been seen
OL,11,Felsewhere.
OL,13,F"However we are still playing catch up
OL,14,Fafter years when there was no increase
OL,15,Fin base tariffs under the previous
OL,16,Fregulatory regime. It kept bills
OL,17,Fartificially low, and starved Guernsey
OL,18,FElectricity of the funds to adequately
OL,19,Finvest in the network.
