OL,3,CGuernsey's electricity bills set to
OL,4,Crise by 10% this summer
OL,6,F"Customers now are having to pay the
OL,7,Fprice of that, so we do not repeat
OL,8,Fthat mistake and burden future
OL,9,Fconsumers.
OL,11,FGuernsey Electricity originally
OL,12,Fapplied for an increase of 12%,
OL,13,Fhowever this was reduced by the States.
OL,15,FDeputy Roffey continued: "The STSB has
OL,16,Ftherefore acted responsibly in
OL,17,Fapproving an increase, although not to
OL,18,Fthe level that Guernsey Electricity
OL,19,Fhad requested.
